metadata.name: Man in the Mirror: First NFT
metadata.description:
Work conceived in its content and design for the format NFTBook, collectible in separate parts, limited edition.

Contemporary reflections to awaken critical thinking.

In this NFTBook the author invites you to a dialogue on 25 topics among others:

The end of communication the beginning of human connectivity.
A change in the space.
Blockchain, the passport to the Noosphere.
Honesty as a way
The future of humanity
	           	       	 
               	 	  	          	    	 	         	 	  	          	    	 	        To look in the mirror is to know yourself. The best way to harmonize with yourself and the environment. 

Shall we connect?
